## Common Tasks

### Updating Movie Posters
When movie posters are missing or broken, run:
```bash
node scripts/update-movie-posters.js
```

This script:
1. Fetches all movies from Sanity
2. Tests if existing poster URLs work
3. Searches TMDb API for correct poster URLs
4. Outputs which movies need updates (or updates them if SANITY_TOKEN env var is set)

You can also use the Sanity MCP tools to manually patch `externalCoverUrl` on shelfItem documents.

